      "description": "Offering an exceptional E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This specimen boasts a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a 3.62 limited-slip differential. Mechanically flawless, the vehicle has undergone documented rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural longevity. The suspension utilizes OEM Sachs dampers and fresh bushings for factory-spec turn-in. Finished in original paint with consistent micron readings, the interior displays zero bolster wear, reflecting its climate-controlled storage history. A true turn-key investment for the discerning driver.",
